---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const metadata = {
  title: "Privacy Policy - Wortaso",
  description: "Privacy Policy for Wortaso",
};
---

<BaseLayout {metadata}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground italic mb-10">Last updated: 16.02.2026</p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is handled when you use the Wortaso mobile
      application ("the App").
    </p>
    <p class="mb-8">
      By using the App, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      I have developed Wortaso as a free educational application for learning German articles. The App is provided
      at no cost and is intended for use "as is".
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Protecting your privacy is very important to me. This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected,
      used, and safeguarded when you use the App.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">2. Data Controller (Contact Information)</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">The data controller responsible for this App is:</p>
    <p class="mb-4"><strong>Name: Amin Rashidbeigi</strong></p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or data protection, please contact me using the
      email below.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">3. Information Collection and Use</h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.1 No Personal Data Collection</h3>
    <p class="mb-4">The App does not collect, store, transmit, or process any personal data.</p>
    <p class="mb-3">Specifically:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li><strong class="text-foreground">No Registration:</strong> You are not required to create an account or provide any personal information.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-foreground">No Analytics or Tracking:</strong> The App does not use third-party analytics tools, tracking technologies, or monitoring services (e.g., Google Analytics, Firebase, or similar).</li>
      <li><strong class="text-foreground">No Advertising:</strong> The App does not display advertisements and does not use advertising identifiers.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-foreground">No Marketing:</strong> No marketing or profiling activities are performed.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">3.2 Local Device Data</h3>
    <p class="mb-3">Any learning progress, preferences, or usage data are stored locally on your device only. This data:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Remains on your device</li>
      <li>Is not transmitted to any server</li>
      <li>Is not accessible to me</li>
      <li>Can be deleted by uninstalling the App</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">4. Third-Party Services (Apple App Store)</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App is distributed via the Apple App Store. Apple may collect certain technical and usage-related
      information in accordance with its own privacy practices. This may include:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Device information</li>
      <li>Operating system version</li>
      <li>Download statistics</li>
      <li>Performance data</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">I do not receive access to any personally identifiable information collected by Apple.</p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      For more information, please review Apple's Privacy Policy:<br />
      <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" class="text-primary hover:underline">
        https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">5. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This App is available within the European Union and complies with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Since no personal data is processed by the App, there is generally no data processing within the meaning of
      Article 6 GDPR.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">Where technically necessary, the legal basis for minimal processing is:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Article 6(1)(f) GDPR – Legitimate interest in providing a secure, functional, and privacy-friendly educational service.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">6. Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
    <p class="mb-3">
      If personal data were to be processed in the future, you would have the following rights under the GDPR:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>Right of access (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to rectification (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to erasure (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
      <li>Right to object (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Currently, since no personal data is collected or stored, these rights generally do not apply in practice.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have concerns about data protection, you may contact me using the information provided above.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">7. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Appropriate technical and organizational measures are taken to ensure that the App operates securely and
      that no unauthorized access to user data occurs.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Because no personal data is transmitted or stored externally, the risk of data misuse is minimized.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      The App does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. Since no personal
      data is collected at all, the App complies with applicable child protection and privacy regulations.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">If you believe that a child has provided personal information, please contact me immediately.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to reflect legal, technical, or functional changes.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Any updates will be published within the App and/or on this page. The "Last updated" date will be revised
      accordingly.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">You are encouraged to review this Privacy Policy periodically.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have any questions, feedback, or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact:
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Email:</strong>{" "}
      <a href="mailto:wortasoapp@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">wortasoapp@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
